Hangman

Program chooses random word from dictionary
Random word substituted for blank characters
Asks for input to guess a letter 
Verifies input is a letter, if not gives error
Checks if letter is in word- if so replaces blank with letter, if not asks choose again
Keeps track of how many guesses player has (optional)
Input option to guess full correct word
Once guessed correctly or all letters guessed, output 'You win!'
Remembers same word through guesses- does not choose another word until player wins or presses 'Give up'
